Josie Rozell is a sophomore English Education major PERIOD This is her first semester writing blog entries for The Bulletin although she has maintained an active blog site for longer PERIOD She is a hopeless Surrealist a passionate advocate and a seeker of perspective PERIOD In her spare time Josie loves running long distances listening to husky Nina Simone and drinking strong dark coffee PERIOD Sometimes all at the same time PERIOD After graduating in May of  Josie would like to join the Peace Corps and eventually find herself teaching English to students all around the world PERIOD
